{"tid":2298785,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自由黨為支持政府「確診獎金」 自行撥200萬元加碼 名額500名 連同政府獎金最高9千元","createTime":"2020-11-24T09:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T10:27:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4575ac463757dffe3b2462b735dcac298c87c7e0","tid":2298785,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"自由黨啟動「關懷基金」補貼多個行業合資格從業員<br />\n<br />\n自由黨表示，支持政府為沒有薪病假受僱或自僱的確診患者，派發一筆過5000元的津貼，並會啟動該黨的「關懷基金」，撥出200萬元，為合資格得到政府津貼的航運交通業、飲食業、零售及批發界、紡織及製衣業界的從業員再提供4000元補貼，名額暫定為500名，不排除會籌集更多資金，讓更多人受惠。<br />\n<br />\n飲食界議員張宇人說，「關懷基金」是希望在合適時間配合政府，希望政府能分辨確診患者是否屬4個行業當中，並協助他們連同政府的5000元津貼，將一共9000元的津貼向合資格患者發放。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561659-20201124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561659-20201124.htm&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaAx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=ce41b462\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561659-20201124.htm&h=13f7e49a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561659-20201124.htm</a>"},{"pid":"45adc5c4461d3cd7ec9c3ad6ac28f49d6cdc3760","tid":2298785,"uid":46154,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:41:28.000Z","msg":"收武肺確診口水，面交"},{"pid":"e0f05feae1a8dbc3d96d35b84f7523af9e9bc6eb","tid":2298785,"uid":68689,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:43:37.000Z","msg":"等睇500收一樽口水可即場交收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6773a53f0fc23d07ef31790c3027569a286d4354","tid":2298785,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"即時炒到上3000"},{"pid":"487aefdd90e887cf2dcc6a43555ffb464cadea41","tid":2298785,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"琴日口水價值每公克跌穿5蚊 而家又彈返上去<img src=\"/asse